race.comment: KELLY JANE (8) finished well back at Healesville last time when a 7 length fifth (19.74) but scored five back at Geelong (25.79). Has a good record here at this journey. Goes well out of this box with a win and five minor placings. Worth another chance. BLINKED (6) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing sixth (24.93) in a Grade 5 at Sale. Form here sound including four wins. Has ability and can measure up. HOCUS POCUS (7) missed the frame last time when fifth (29.95) at Sandown in a Grade 5 but not beaten far the start prior. Well placed here and can atone this time. SWEET NUGGET (1) has top-three aspirations after placing at big odds last time.
